{"tid":1396702,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要做到罷市，難度有幾高？","createTime":"2019-08-02T07:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:50:04.000Z","uid":20948,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64647a16642579c99e214b540f1ca4b358396898","tid":1396702,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"大家都喺度講<span style=\"color: red;\">罷工，罷買，攬炒，</span><br />\n但其實我地心入面都知道，要香港人無限期罷工，根本連解放軍都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷一日係可以做到，但罷工一日，對政府造成威脅有限<br />\n香港最大籌碼一直都係金融，<span style=\"color: gold;\">人民幣最大結算口，外資走入中國重要通道</span>。<br />\n要政府怯，最直接就係罷市，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果個市停返一星期，外資肯定雞飛狗走，恆指大幅波動，隨時引發支爆</span></span><br />\n但問題係，要罷市真係好難，<br />\n首先要locate到所有primiry同redundant嘅data centre，用某啲方法令到佢停止運作，<br />\n之後仲要用各種方法令金融區返唔到工，儘量拖延開市。<br />\n開唔到市，對香港嘅影響可以話係大過曬其他，政府除左要<span style=\"color: red;\">用盡方法開返市</span>，更加要<span style=\"color: red;\">安撫外資唔好撤離香港</span>，要令佢地<span style=\"color: gold;\">對香港恢復信心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"aea01898e75fe853d6607c989105196e87e5d36b","tid":1396702,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b502a7d334d8c216414a1039ede24e9ff9421060","tid":1396702,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aea01898e75fe853d6607c989105196e87e5d36b","tid":1396702,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:38:41.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid